metadata.name: Froggy Dreams
metadata.description:
First (and probably last) longer animation made by Matt Crabe. through the wonders of technology we can watch this frog dream. It seems the frogs dreams are more like nightmares, but the frog is content with any type of dream entertainment, no matter how terrifying.

Froggy Dreams has been created for Dalbin Table.  
This NFT is auctioned on SuperRare separately from the Table.  
Buy your Table in the Dalbin Store and import your NFT art collection.  
The file resolution is 3840 x 2160 px (4K UHD).  
More info: dalbin.com
